    <title>On the comparison of nearby cycles via $b$-functions</title>
    <summary>  In this article, we give a simple proof of the comparison of nearby and
vanishing cycles in the sense of Riemann-Hilbert correspondence following the
idea of Beilinson and Bernstein, without using the Kashiwara-Malgrange
$V$-filtrations.
</summary>
